### **3. 25_LogEchoScanner**  
**Description:**  
A command-line tool that scans logs and highlights repeated error lines.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogEchoScanner - Pattern-Finding Log Parser

LogEchoScanner finds repetitive entries and key error indicators in long log files.

## Features
- Highlights frequent lines  
- Simple summary view  
- Works with rotated logs  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_LogEchoScanner.git
cd 25_LogEchoScanner
python analyze.py /path/to/logfile.log
